OL,5, It was a simple at-home DNA testing    
OL,6, kit, a Christmas day gift, that upended
OL,7, the lives of two Canadian men forever. 
OL,9,FRichard Beauvais, from the coastal town
OL,10,Fof Sechelt, British Columbia, grew up  
OL,11,Fhis whole life believing he was        
OL,12,Findigenous. But the test he took showed
OL,13,Fthat he had a mix of Ukrainian,        
OL,14,FAshkenazi Jewish and Polish ancestry.  
OL,16,FAround the same time and nearly 1,500  
OL,17,Fmiles (2,400km) away, the sister of    
OL,18,FEddy Ambrose from Winnipeg, Manitoba,  
OL,19,Fwho was raised in a Ukrainian family,  
OL,20,Falso took a DNA test, and discovered   
OL,21,Fthat she was not related to Eddy.      
